omaly from 2025-06-24T14:10:44Z to 2025-06-24T14:33:44Z. Please infer the possible cause.", "time_range": "2025-06-24 14:10:44+00:00 to 2025-06-24 14:33:44+00:00"}, "log_analysis_findings": "基于收集到的日志数据，我现在进行分析。从日志中可以识别出明显的连接问题模式。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"connection refused\", \"dial tcp\", \"port\", \"context canceled\", \"timed out\", \"Unavailable\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"223.193.36.56:32187\",\n      \"reason\": \"端口配置错误或服务不可用，导致多个服务连接被拒绝\",\n      \"evidence\": \"dial tcp 223.193.36.56:32187: connect: connection refused\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"currencyservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"货币服务连接超时和上下文取消，影响订单处理\",\n      \"evidence\": \"failed to convert currency: rpc error: code = Unavailable desc = timed out waiting for server handshake\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**分析发现**：\n\n1. **主要问题**：多个frontend服务和productcatalogservice都报告连接到 `223.193.36.56:32187` 时出现 `connection refused` 错误\n2. **影响范围**：\n   - frontend服务无法获取产品信息（productcatalogservice）\n   - frontend服务无法获取产品推荐\n   - 订单结算时货币转换服务超时\n3. **关键特征**：\n   - 符合端口配置错误模式（connection refused + 目标IP:端口）\n   - 出现连接超时和上下文取消错误\n   - 影响多个服务的正常功能\n\n根据端口配置错误识别规则，被调方服务（运行在223.193.36.56:32187的服务）是根因组件。", "trace_analysis_findings": "基于Trace数据的分析，我已经识别出了系统异常的根本原因。以下是详细分析：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\"rrt_max\", \"error_ratio\", \"frontend->productcatalogservice\", \"checkoutservice->currencyservice\", \"productcatalogservice->TiDB\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"检测到大量连接拒绝错误：'dial tcp 223.193.36.56:32187: connect: connection refused'，涉及多个frontend到productcatalogservice的调用\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"currencyservice\", \n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"CurrencyService/GetSupportedCurrencies调用延迟从正常的2.96秒激增至3687万秒，出现超时握手错误\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"TiDB数